OL,3,CFamilies turning to crowdfunding and
OL,4,Cloan sharks to pay for funerals `
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FBereaved families are turning to
OL,8,Fcrowdfunding and loan sharks to pay
OL,9,Ffor funerals as the cost of a
OL,10,Ftraditional service saw its biggest
OL,11,Fannual increase since 2016, according
OL,12,Fto an annual report.
OL,14,FThe cost of a traditional attended
OL,15,Ffuneral jumped 5.3% to #4,510 last
OL,16,Fyear, SunLife's latest Cost of Dying
OL,17,FReport said.
