OL,3,CFamilies turning to crowdfunding and
OL,4,Cloan sharks to pay for funerals `
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FA simple attended funeral, which
OL,8,Fincludes the core elements of a
OL,9,Ftraditional service but with fewer add-
OL,10,Fons such as a memorial and flowers, is
OL,11,Fnow the most common choice in the UK,
OL,12,Fcosting an average of #3,828.
OL,14,FWhen teamed with a memorial, catering,
OL,15,Fvenue hire and flowers, total spending
OL,16,Fon the average funeral rose to #5,140.
OL,18,FRising prices have been driven by
OL,19,Fincreased cremation and burial fees,
OL,20,Fhigher coffin prices, and increased
OL,21,Fliving costs.
