OL,3,CFamilies turning to crowdfunding and
OL,4,Cloan sharks to pay for funerals `
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FSome 15% of families say they have
OL,8,Ffaced financial hardship paying for a
OL,9,Ffuneral, having to find an extra
OL,10,F#2,365 on average.
OL,12,FMore than one in 10 (12%) of those
OL,13,Ffacing financial difficulty turned to
OL,14,Fcrowdfunding to cover funeral costs,
OL,15,Fwhile 8% reported borrowing money from
OL,16,Fan unregulated lender or loan shark.
OL,18,FLondon remains the most expensive
OL,19,Fplace to die, with the cost of a
OL,20,Fsimple attended funeral averaging
OL,21,F#4,897.
