OL,3,CFamilies turning to crowdfunding and
OL,4,Cloan sharks to pay for funerals `
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FThe report found that those who knew
OL,8,Fsome of the deceased's funeral
OL,9,Fpreferences were able to save an
OL,10,Faverage of #335 on a send-off compared
OL,11,Fwith those who did not.
OL,13,FMeanwhile, direct cremations, costing
OL,14,Fan average of #1,628, are now chosen
OL,15,Ffor 21% of funerals ` with the
OL,16,Fmajority of cases involving the
OL,17,Fdeceased having planned the
OL,18,Farrangements.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
