OL,3,CFamilies turning to crowdfunding and
OL,4,Cloan sharks to pay for funerals `
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FHowever 86% of those who opted for a
OL,8,Fdirect cremation still chose to hold a
OL,9,Fmemorial, wake or celebration of life,
OL,10,Fbringing the full spending to an
OL,11,Faverage of #2,949.
OL,13,FSome 70% of people make some form of
OL,14,Fprovision for their funeral to ease
OL,15,Fthe burden on those left behind, such
OL,16,Fas savings, funeral plans, and life
OL,17,Finsurance, the study found.
OL,19,FJust 42% save enough to cover the full
OL,20,Fcost, leaving loved ones to bridge the
OL,21,Fgap.
