OL,3,CFamilies turning to crowdfunding and
OL,4,Cloan sharks to pay for funerals `
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FSunLife chief executive Mark Screeton
OL,8,Fsaid: "Funerals are a deeply personal
OL,9,Fexperience, but our research shows
OL,10,Fthat the cost of saying goodbye
OL,11,Fcontinues to rise faster than some
OL,12,Ffamilies can afford.
OL,14,F"We are seeing more people turning to
OL,15,Fsimple attended funerals, a modern
OL,16,Fmiddle ground between traditional and
OL,17,Fdirect options, allowing families to
OL,18,Fcelebrate their loved one's life
OL,19,Fwithout overspending.
